      <title>Screen Recording on iPhone Made Easy</title>
      <link>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/how-to-record-iphone-screen/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 09:16:52 &#43;0700</pubDate>
      <guid>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/how-to-record-iphone-screen/</guid>
      <description>To record your iPhone screen, go to Settings &amp;gt; Control Center, then tap the &amp;lsquo;+&amp;rsquo; icon next to Screen Recording. Open the Control Center and tap the Screen Recording icon, then wait for the countdown to finish. You can stop the recording by going back to the Control Center and tapping the Screen Recording icon again.</description>
